page.title: 07SOME HOUSES IN MY STREET
page.content: The first house is on the right,it is semi_detatched and has a normal brick wall.It has a garage & a fence all around the back garden & a wall around the front garden. Next is my house,it has an extension of one floor,which consists of a garage,a lounge,a bathroom,a lobby & a utility room.It has a wall around the front garden that is also brick. On the left of the road,the first house has trees all round the back garden,no wall or fence around the front garden.It does not have a garage,just a driveway.It has a sort of porch with no doors but it has a roof over the door.The next house on the left has a fence round the front garden,it has a driveway and a side_ way.It has a porch and an extension on the back and a big pond in the back garden.
